<br>
Zone out of Crystal Caves into box with crystal to resow.<br>
Hit Track and see like 8-10 Royal Archers.<br>
Think, damn, I missed it again.<br>
Walk out and find the Archers on the small hill.<br>
Walk past them and find the Royal Priest or something with a few other named ones standing around.<br>
Think, well, guess I did miss it and walk back toward fort.<br>
Then I see all the Elites/Oracles/Giants in rows in front of the fort and think Woohoo!<br>
Improve Camo myself and walk in the fort.<br>
I see The Oracle and Fizant Black. I almost kill Fizant, but he was only wielding one Dark Ember, and I was really interested in the shield, so I move over to the other side and ensnare/dot/root him. He really only had like 4-5k of hp, not much. Was little problem to kill him. And of course he dropped the shield. I will start using it after I get my epic friend. I am currently balanced at 200 wisdom and would lose 3 wisdom going to the shield, from my Book of Obulus. After I get my epic I will have like 15 wisdom to decide what to do with, so I think the first think will be the shield =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvalinn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valinn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/2/01 9:31:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where Rygorr Oracle Shield?</span><hr size=1> It doesn't drop from the Orcs/Giants out on the 'patio' =)<br>
<br>
As part of the quest, the chief, oracle, firbrand and a couple others spawn apart from the main force of the battle.  These have the goodies.<br>
<br>
Valinn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulemmingg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lemmingg</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/6/01 8:34:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where Rygorr Oracle Shield?</span><hr size=1> Does he always drop the shield?<br>
